quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  19,39,"Kulɓinir ɓe ñande Nimse, tuma nde fiyaake on ñaawaa hara kamɓe hiɓe e ndeer welsindaare hara ɓe gooŋɗinaa."
  19,40,"Minen min ndonat lesdi ndi e ɓen wonɓe e dow mayri, ko ka amen ɓe nduttetee."
  19,41,"Jaŋto ka deftere Ibraahiima, pellet, kaŋko o laatino Goonguɗo annabaajo."
  19,42,"Tuma nde o maakannoo bem makko: "eeyma baaba ko holɗum ndewantaa ɗum ko nanataa yi'ataa hara duncantaa ma hay e hu'unde?"
  19,43,"Eeyma baaba min dey gooɗii arii am immorde e Ganndal kon ko araani e maaɗa, jokkam mi fewne e Laawol po'occiingol."
  19,44,"Eeyma baaba, wota a rew Seytaane, pellet, Seytaane laatike jedduɗo jurmotooɗo."
  19,45,"Eeyma baaba, min dey miɗo huli wota meeme Lepte immorde ka jurmotooɗo laatanoɗaa Seytaane giɗo."
  19,46,"[Baaba makko] wi'i: "Enee, an a añ deweteeɗi am ɗin nee Ibraahiima, pellet, si a accaani mi fiɗete selam dummunne [juutuɗo]."
  19,47,"[Ibraahiima] maaki: "Kisal e maaɗa aray mi inminanomaa ka Joomi am, pellet, Koŋko O Laatike Newaniiɗo kam."
  19,48,"Mi martoo(deestoo) on e kon ko ndewoton ga Alla, mi toroo Joomi am no gasa mi wonataa tampirɗo toragol Joomi am."
  19,49,"Tuma nde o martinoo(deestinoo) ɓe e ko ɓe ndewata kon gaAlla, min n ngokki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba kala [gooto e maɓɓe] Men waɗi [mo] Annabaajo."
  19,50,"Min ngokki ɓe immorde e Yurmeende amen, min mbaɗani ɓe mantoore toownde."
  19,51,"Jaŋto ka deftere Muusaa, pellet, kaŋko o laatinoke laɓɓinɗo o laatinoke kadi Nulaaɗo Annabiijo."